"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-12-Sun-Yingsha-represents-Asia-at-Paris-Olympics-closing-ceremony-1w0tA0cyyWY-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha attends the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame during the Paris Olympics closing ceremony on August 11, 2024. /IC  Chinese table tennis athlete Sun Yingsha took the stage as the representative of Asian athletes during the closing ceremony of the Paris Olympics on Sunday.  She joined athletes from around the world in the symbolic extinguishing of the Olympic flame, marking the end of the 16-day global sporting spectacle.  The 23-year-old secured two gold and one silver medals at the Paris Olympics.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9